---
// Hero Section - Hook + CTA + VSL
---

<section class="min-h-screen bg-brand-dark flex items-center pt-20 pb-12">
  <div class="section-container">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <!-- Left: Copy -->
        <div class="space-y-8 text-center lg:text-left">
          <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight text-brand-text">
            You delegate everything else. Stop DIY-ing your body.
          </h1>

          <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl text-brand-muted">
            You've got systems. Delegation. Dashboards. Things running while you sleep. The one thing that decides if you're operating at full capacity or just surviving your schedule and you're winging it.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-brand-gray border-l-4 border-brand-accent p-6 sm:p-8 text-left">
            <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-brand-text">
              <span class="text-brand-accent font-semibold">Result: </span>
              Six months from now: Sharp. Focused when it counts. Present for what matters. And you finally look like what you've built.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center lg:justify-start flex-wrap">
            <a
              href="/why-nothings-worked"
              class="btn-primary text-base sm:text-lg py-4 px-8 sm:px-10 w-full sm:w-auto text-center"
            >
              Why It Fails
            </a>
            <a
              href="/how-it-works"
              class="btn-primary text-base sm:text-lg py-4 px-8 sm:px-10 w-full sm:w-auto text-center"
            >
              How It Works
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: VSL Video -->
        <div class="relative lg:order-last order-first">
          <!-- Placeholder for VSL video -->
          <div class="aspect-video bg-brand-gray rounded-lg border-2 border-brand-accent/30 overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
            <div class="w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <!-- TODO: Replace with actual VSL video embed -->
              <div class="text-center space-y-4 p-8">
                <svg class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto text-brand-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.752 11.168l-3.197-2.132A1 1 0 0010 9.87v4.263a1 1 0 001.555.832l3.197-2.132a1 1 0 000-1.664z"></path>
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                </svg>
                <p class="text-brand-muted font-medium">VSL Video</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-center text-brand-muted mt-4 text-sm">90 seconds. Watch this first.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a0a 0%, #1a1a1a 100%);
  }
</style>
